{"generated":"2026-03-30T05:18:20.495252853Z","published":"2023-12-20T00:56:51Z","app":"watchexec","version":"1.24.2","notes":"<p dir=\"auto\"><em>Software development often involves running the same commands over and over. Boring! Watchexec is a simple, standalone tool that watches a path and runs a command whenever it detects modifications. Install it today with <a href=\"https://github.com/cargo-bins/cargo-binstall\"><code class=\"notranslate\">cargo-binstall watchexec-cli</code></a>, from the binaries below, find it <a href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/blob/main/doc/packages.md\">in your favourite package manager</a>, or build it from source with <code class=\"notranslate\">cargo install watchexec-cli</code>.</em></p>\n<h4 dir=\"auto\">In this release:</h4>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Fix queueing behaviour (<a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"2037296973\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/726\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/issues/726/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/726\">#726</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"2048438228\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/734\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/pull/734/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/pull/734\">#734</a>, <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"2048462946\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/735\" data-hovercard-type=\"pull_request\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/pull/735/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/pull/735\">#735</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 dir=\"auto\">Other changes:</h4>